s.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Ibrahim-Al-Dossari/068038.mp3","05":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Misyari-Rasyid-Al-Afasi/068038.mp3"}},{"nomorAyat":39,"teksArab":"اَمْ لَكُمْ اَيْمَانٌ عَلَيْنَا بَالِغَةٌ اِلٰى يَوْمِ الْقِيٰمَةِۙ اِنَّ لَكُمْ لَمَا تَحْكُمُوْنَۚ","teksLatin":"am lakum aimānun ‘alainā bāligatun ilā yaumil-qiyāmah(ti), inna lakum lamā taḥkumūn(a).","teksIndonesia":"Atau apakah kamu memperoleh (janji-janji yang diperkuat dengan) sumpah dari Kami, yang tetap berlaku sampai hari Kiamat; bahwa kamu dapat mengambil keputusan (sekehendakmu)? ","audio":{"01":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdullah-Al-Juhany/068039.mp3","02":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdul-Muhsin-Al-Qasim/068039.mp3","03":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdurrahman-as-Sudais/068039.mp3","04":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Ibrahim-Al-Dossari/068039.mp3","05":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Misyari-Rasyid-Al-Afasi/068039.mp3"}},{"nomorAyat":40,"teksArab":"سَلْهُمْ اَيُّهُمْ بِذٰلِكَ زَعِيْمٌۚ","teksLatin":"salhum ayyuhum biżālika za‘īm(un).","teksIndonesia":"Tanyakanlah kepada mereka, “Siapakah di antara mereka yang bertanggung jawab terhadap (keputusan yang diambil itu)?”","audio":{"01":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdullah-Al-Juhany/068040.mp3","02":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdul-Muhsin-Al-Qasim/068040.mp3","03":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdurrahman-as-Sudais/068040.mp3","04":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Ibrahim-Al-Dossari/068040.mp3","05":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Misyari-Rasyid-Al-Afasi/068040.mp3"}},{"nomorAyat":41,"teksArab":"اَمْ لَهُمْ شُرَكَاۤءُۚ فَلْيَأْتُوْا بِشُرَكَاۤىِٕهِمْ اِنْ كَانُوْا صٰدِقِيْنَ ","teksLatin":"am lahum syurakā'(u), falya'tū bisyurakā'ihim in kānū ṣādiqīn(a).","teksIndonesia":"Atau apakah mereka mempunyai sekutu-sekutu? Kalau begitu hendaklah mereka mendatangkan sekut