partial/Ibrahim-Al-Dossari/068043.mp3","05":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Misyari-Rasyid-Al-Afasi/068043.mp3"}},{"nomorAyat":44,"teksArab":"فَذَرْنِيْ وَمَنْ يُّكَذِّبُ بِهٰذَا الْحَدِيْثِۗ سَنَسْتَدْرِجُهُمْ مِّنْ حَيْثُ لَا يَعْلَمُوْنَۙ","teksLatin":"fażarnī wa may yukażżibu bihāżal-ḥadīṡi sanastadrijuhum min ḥaiṡu lā ya‘lamūn(a).","teksIndonesia":"Maka serahkanlah kepada-Ku (urusannya) dan orang-orang yang mendustakan perkataan ini (Al-Qur'an). Kelak akan Kami hukum mereka berangsur-angsur dari arah yang tidak mereka ketahui, ","audio":{"01":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdullah-Al-Juhany/068044.mp3","02":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdul-Muhsin-Al-Qasim/068044.mp3","03":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdurrahman-as-Sudais/068044.mp3","04":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Ibrahim-Al-Dossari/068044.mp3","05":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Misyari-Rasyid-Al-Afasi/068044.mp3"}},{"nomorAyat":45,"teksArab":"وَاُمْلِيْ لَهُمْۗ اِنَّ كَيْدِيْ مَتِيْنٌ ","teksLatin":"wa umlī lahum, inna kaidī matīn(un).","teksIndonesia":"dan Aku memberi tenggang waktu kepada mereka. Sungguh, rencana-Ku sangat teguh. ","audio":{"01":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdullah-Al-Juhany/068045.mp3","02":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdul-Muhsin-Al-Qasim/068045.mp3","03":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdurrahman-as-Sudais/068045.mp3","04":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Ibrahim-Al-Dossari/068045.mp3","05":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Misyari-Rasyid-Al-Afasi/068045.mp3"}},{"nomorAyat":46,"teksArab":"اَمْ تَسْـَٔلُهُمْ اَجْرًا فَهُمْ مِّنْ مَّغْرَمٍ مُّثْقَلُوْنَۚ ","teksLatin":"am tas'aluhum ajran fahum mim magramim muṡqalūn(a).","teksIndonesia":"Ataukah engkau (Muhammad) meminta imbalan kepada mereka, sehingga mereka dibebani dengan utang?","audio":{"01":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdullah-Al-