tadārakahū ni‘matum mir rabbihī lanubiża bil-‘arā'i wa huwa mażmūm(un).","teksIndonesia":"Sekiranya dia tidak segera mendapat nikmat dari Tuhannya, pastilah dia dicampakkan ke tanah tandus dalam keadaan tercela. ","audio":{"01":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdullah-Al-Juhany/068049.mp3","02":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdul-Muhsin-Al-Qasim/068049.mp3","03":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdurrahman-as-Sudais/068049.mp3","04":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Ibrahim-Al-Dossari/068049.mp3","05":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Misyari-Rasyid-Al-Afasi/068049.mp3"}},{"nomorAyat":50,"teksArab":"فَاجْتَبٰىهُ رَبُّهٗ فَجَعَلَهٗ مِنَ الصّٰلِحِيْنَ ","teksLatin":"fajtabāhu rabbuhū faja‘alahū minaṣ-ṣāliḥīn(a).","teksIndonesia":"Lalu Tuhannya memilihnya dan menjadikannya termasuk orang yang saleh. ","audio":{"01":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdullah-Al-Juhany/068050.mp3","02":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdul-Muhsin-Al-Qasim/068050.mp3","03":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdurrahman-as-Sudais/068050.mp3","04":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Ibrahim-Al-Dossari/068050.mp3","05":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Misyari-Rasyid-Al-Afasi/068050.mp3"}},{"nomorAyat":51,"teksArab":"وَاِنْ يَّكَادُ الَّذِيْنَ كَفَرُوْا لَيُزْلِقُوْنَكَ بِاَبْصَارِهِمْ لَمَّا سَمِعُوا الذِّكْرَ وَيَقُوْلُوْنَ اِنَّهٗ لَمَجْنُوْنٌ ۘ","teksLatin":"wa iy yakādul-lażīna kafarū layuzliqūnaka bi'abṣārihim lammā sami‘uż żikra wa yaqūlūna innahū lamajnūn(un).","teksIndonesia":"Dan sungguh, orang-orang kafir itu hampir-hampir menggelincirkanmu dengan pandangan mata mereka, ketika mereka mendengar Al-Qur'an dan mereka berkata, “Dia (Muhammad) itu benar-benar orang gila.”","audio":{"01":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdullah-Al-Juhany/068051.mp3","02":"https://equran.nos.wjv-1.neo.id/audio-partial/Abdul-Muhsin-Al-Qasim/068051.mp3","03"